<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Simtree Credit Coupon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .coupon-container {
            background-color: #f0f5ff;
            border: 2px dashed #4c6ef5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .coupon-amount {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4c6ef5;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .coupon-code {
            background-color: #4c6ef5;
            color: white;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            display: inline-block;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .instructions {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4c6ef5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .expires {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Simtree eSIM Platform</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>You've Received a Credit Coupon!</h2>
            
            <p>Hello,</p>
            
            <p>You have received a credit coupon for your Simtree eSIM Platform account. You can use this coupon to add credit to your wallet.</p>
            
            <div class="coupon-container">
                <h3>YOUR COUPON</h3>
                <div class="coupon-amount">${{amount}}</div>
                <div class="coupon-code">{{code}}</div>
                {{#if expiryDate}}
                <div class="expires">Expires on: {{expiryDate}}</div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>How to redeem your coupon:</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li>Log in to your Simtree eSIM Platform account</li>
                    <li>Go to the Wallet section</li>
                    <li>Enter your coupon code in the "Redeem Coupon" field</li>
                    <li>Click "Redeem" to add the credit to your account</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for using Simtree eSIM Platform!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Simtree eSIM Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>